content: 've been texting for several days. I verified my phone # a few days ago. The only threads under Text Team are texting questions and texting nice things. I logged out and back in but that didn't help. Please advise.
Hi Alena, you should have access. Go to Channels & Roles and click browse channels. Check to see if all the text channels are selected on there!
You can find this section at the top left under Server Guide & the Events tab. Let me know if that fixes it
Thanks. They were checked off already, but I see those 2 channels now. Thanks
Perfect! Discord can be a bit whacky sometimes but we're here to help if you need anything else. Thanks for being here!
